OL,6,FSinn Fein and the DUP have been
OL,7,Faccused of showing a lack of respect
OL,8,Fon the issue of child poverty after
OL,9,Fthe SDLP criticised their turnout at
OL,10,Fan Assembly Opposition Day debate on
OL,11,Fthe issue.
OL,13,FSDLP MLAs made the claims as they
OL,14,Ftabled a motion calling on Communities
OL,15,FMinister Gordon Lyons to draw up a
OL,16,Fplan to remove the controversial two-
OL,17,Fchild limit on Universal Credit and
OL,18,FChild Tax Credit benefit payments.
