OL,6,FThe SDLP also tabled motions on
OL,7,Feradicating fuel poverty and banning
OL,8,Fno-fault evictions in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FLeader of the Opposition Matthew
OL,11,FO'Toole opened his remarks on the two-
OL,12,Fchild-limit debate by expressing
OL,13,Fregret that only two Sinn Fein and
OL,14,Ffour DUP MLAs, including Minister
OL,15,FLyons, were present in the chamber for
OL,16,Fthe start of proceedings.
