OL,6,F"I am certainly not in any way
OL,7,Fsupporting or defending that two-child
OL,8,Flimit, I don't think it is of benefit
OL,9,Fto people here in Northern Ireland,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"I however have to look at the cost of
OL,13,Fwhat mitigating that would be if we
OL,14,Fwere to take that cost on for
OL,15,Fourselves."
