OL,6,FDuring the debate, several MLAs raised
OL,7,Fparticular concerns around the
OL,8,Fpolicy's so-called "rape clause", that
OL,9,Fallows women who give birth to a third
OL,10,For subsequent child as a result of non-
OL,11,Fconsensual sex to claim addition
OL,12,Fbenefit support, but only if they
OL,13,Fprovided evidence confirming they were
OL,14,Fa victim of rape.
OL,16,FMr Lyons branded the clause
OL,17,F"horrendous".
