OL,6,FSinn Fein MLA Colm Gildernew said his
OL,7,Fparty supported offsetting the impact
OL,8,Fof the two-child limit on families in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,F"We believe that this policy
OL,12,Fdiscriminates against women and
OL,13,Fchildren, that it is a key driver of
OL,14,Fchild poverty, and that it
OL,15,Fdisproportionately impacts on people
OL,16,Fhere because of our larger family
OL,17,Fsize," he said.
