OL,6,FA DUP amendment to the SDLP motion
OL,7,Fdeleted the call for the minister to
OL,8,Fbring forward a plan to remove the two-
OL,9,Fchild limit by the end of 2024 and
OL,10,Freplaced it with calls for him to
OL,11,Fconsider the merits of a proposal to
OL,12,Foffset the payment cap with a Better
OL,13,FStart Larger Families payment.
OL,15,FMembers backed the amendment by 69
OL,16,Fvotes to 10, with the amended motion
OL,17,Fthen passing without objection on an
OL,18,Foral vote.
